1937;;Command Performance;;British;;Sinclair Hill;;Arthur Tracy, Lilli Palmer;;musical;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command_Performance_(1937_film);;Growing tired of his life of fame, a singer runs away from a domineering manager and goes to live with a group of gypsies. A massive manhunt is whipped by the press to find him so that he can shoot the final scenes of his latest film.